column5: Was out early this morning for some fresh air. It's 363 days 'til Christmas and people already have their Christmas lights up. What gives?
but its only a few days until Ukrainian Christmas!
but its only a few days until Ukrainian Christmas!  Thanks, ok that makes sense. I was confused.
My neighbour put his up a few days ago.  Darn things will be going till late March.
I didn't even bother this year.  Everyone else puts theirs up in November and leaves them up until June around here
Way to go Roy!  Easy to see you have too much time on your hands!
